name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForCerebrovascularAccident
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Cerebrovascular Accident
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to cerebrovascular accident (cerebral infarction/stroke).),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes ischemic and hemorrhagic strokes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes transient ischemic attack and sequelae or complications of cerebral infarction.)
